Startup plugin for phonegap.
----------------------------

Allows smooth transitions between different views/actions. 

Installation:

iPhone:
1) Copy Transition.m and Transition.h to folder Plugins
2) Include transition.js in your index.html   

Android:
1) Include Android/src as source-Folder in your project.
2) Copy res/values/loading_spinner.xml in your projects res-folder. (Style for centered progress dialog without border)
3) Add the import for your resource Java file (yourpackage.R) to LoadingSpinner.java
4) Include Android/js/transition.js in your index.html


Usage:
1) Call initTransition() on startup of the app.
2) Call showLoadingView() to show the loading view. (Android: can use parameter "animation" ('slide' oder 'fade'))
3) When the animation has finished 'transitionAnimationReady' is fired.
4) Call hideLoadingView() to hide the loading view.






